---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-[#050507] text-gray-500 py-16 border-t border-white/5 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold tracking-wider mb-4 text-sm">NF COFFEE SYSTEMS</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 max-w-sm leading-relaxed">Platform peracikan ekosistem kopi modern generasi terbaru dengan dedikasi cita rasa tinggi.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-white font-medium text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Navigation</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home Base</a></li>
        <li><a href="#menu" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Catalog Grid</a></li>
        <li><a href="#fitur" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Core Value</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-white font-medium text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Operational Hub</h4>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Makassar, South Sulawesi<br/>
        Waktu Operasional: 09:00 - 22:00 WITA
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-[11px]">
    <div>&copy; {currentYear} NF Coffee Studio. Built with Astro & Tailwind v4.</div>
    <div class="flex gap-6">
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">Privacy Protocol</a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">Terms of Service</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>